message:
feat: add event details view (#381)

* events: store and display event metadata

Adds a modal that displays information like which relays the event
came from.

* relays: only subscribe to enabled relays

* Limits subs to enabled + hinted relays. It used to include disabled
  relays.
* Ignore AUTH calls from relays that aren't on the user's listed relays.
  Mostly those will be from unknown relays and user can't auth anyway,
  but it would pop up the signing screen anyway.

Improve the quoted message UI and new / reply message form (#176)

* Improve the quoted message UI

* Lower the contrast prominence of the quoted message
* Fix the vertical alignment

* Highlight the "new message" text area to make it more visible

* Optimize the reply / new message button

* Highlight the send button with a background color
* On mobile add the "send_message" text to the new message button
* Optimize the textarea border

author: lvlr
message:
LocalState: awaitable put(), logic fix, doCallbacks() uses _.debounce, not _.throttle.

Note: linting does not like having an extra object as the third argument
of the _.debounce call, but following how linter suggests to fix it, makes it
look worse to me. Ideas on how to format this better?

author: mmalmi
message:
Localforage (#136)

For State.local we use our very own Fun.ts instead of Gun.js. It's a light version of the Gun api with localForage only persistence. Localstorage is fastest — let's see if it suffices or if we need to change to indexeddb.
